snippet.title: Athena Cykes: Ace Attorney - Locks on the Heart Demo
snippet.description:
The demo for a cancelled fangame, pretty good. Nina Phan and Lydon Case have full sprite sets, Oberon Sesler uses Cody Hackins as a placeholder. Athena and Blackquill have been adapted to 2D.
This demo case is called "Rendezvous at the Turnabout".
Both good and bad endings achieved.
The game can be played here (https://aaonline.fr/player.php?trial_id=104200).
The credits music is Billie Eilish - You Should See Me in a Crown for some reason. Hopefully no region blocking.
